headline: Can Welltower’s 2024 Rally Continue After Strong Q1 Earnings Growth?
summary: Thinking about buying or holding Welltower stock? You are definitely not alone. With the share price recently closing at $172.34 and returning a stunning 38.2% so far in 2024, investors are seeing reasons to keep an eye on this powerhouse in senior housing and healthcare real estate. Over the past three years, Welltower’s returns have absolutely soared, up 213.4%, and the five-year return sits at a hefty 269.3%. Even in the last month, shares climbed another 2.0%, indicating steady optimism...

headline: SL Green's Q3 FFO & Revenues Beat Estimates, Rental Rates Improve
summary: SLG posts a solid third quarter with higher FFO and strong Manhattan leasing, while eyeing major office acquisitions to expand its portfolio.
